845f028610bf10a6b1","tid":1746312,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:20:48.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致 撞區候選人，<br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>申請不反通知書，否則只有零票。</span></span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=b233bdf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add8c09992cd01036a5ee90d5f1de831c2c94116","tid":1746312,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f710250b00d00b514db8dec9590dd0c1176e62a4","tid":1746312,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma